data.description: Discover a stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath home with exceptional features. Dive into luxury with an inviting inground pool and spacious deck, perfect for outdoor gatherings. A brand new roof provides worry-free living, while fresh paint inside and out radiates modern elegance. Step onto brand new carpet that adds comfort to every step. The corner lot location enhances curb appeal and offers extra space. The home showcases stainless appliances, adding a touch of sophistication to the heart of the house. Indulge in comfort, style, and leisure in this remarkable property. With just minutes from the ocean front you will find this location ideal. Schedule your showing today!
